{"product_id":"young-rich-mighty","title":"YOUNG RICH MIGHTY","description":"\u003cp\u003e260 GSM. 100% French Terry Cotton. Gender-Neutral. Relaxed Fit. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed. Premium Puff \u0026amp; Screen Print. Exclusive Limited Edition.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis 260 GSM French terry cotton T-shirt is crafted to combine premium comfort with bold, statement-driven design. Built from heavyweight French terry cotton, the fabric delivers a smooth, structured feel while remaining breathable and durable for all-day wear. Designed as an exclusive limited-edition release, the front features the striking \u003cstrong\u003e“YOUNG RICH MIGHTY”\u003c\/strong\u003e artwork executed in a combination of premium puff and screen printing for layered texture and depth. The back carries the signature \u003cstrong\u003e09\u003c\/strong\u003e brand number in the same high-quality print finish, creating a cohesive, standout identity from every angle. Combed and bio-washed for long-lasting softness and shape retention, this tee is made for those who move with confidence and presence.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors using cold water. Avoid bleach. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to maintain print texture and fabric quality. Do not iron directly on the prints. Store in a cool, dry place.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM French terry cotton for a premium heavyweight structure. Relaxed, gender-neutral fit designed for everyday statement wear. Front “YOUNG RICH MIGHTY” artwork in premium puff and screen print combination. Back brand number 09 executed in matching high-quality print finish. Exclusive limited-edition design for elevated street presence. Combed and bio-washed fabric for enhanced softness, durability, and long-term shape retention.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47500129829018,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47500129861786,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47500129894554,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47500129960090,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":47500129992858,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":47687033159834,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00346copy_1__11zon.jpg?v=1772289837","url":"https:\/\/dripdrip.in\/products\/young-rich-mighty","provider":"DRIP STUDIOS","version":"1.0","type":"link"}